high_descs: Walk forward to the kitchen countertop.
Pick up the egg from the counter just left of the sink.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Heat the egg in the microwave then remove the egg.
Face the countertop just right of the microwave.
Set the egg down on the countertop behind the frying pan.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked Egg on the CounterTop

high_descs: Turn around walk to the right and left of the countertop.
Go to the kitchen countertop and place the egg.
Pick up the egg in the microwave.
Turn around move to the egg in the microwave
Open the countertop in the microwave and turn around.
Move to the egg on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the egg, open the microwave, turn around, and move to the countertop.

high_descs: Go straight head towards the countertop in kitchen.
Take the egg near to the sink.
Turn around then turn right to the microwave.
Put the egg in the oven, heat it, and take it back.
Place the egg on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Take the egg near to the sink heat it and Place it on the CounterTop
